<title>USA: Falcon Building Products completes debt deal.</title>
<headline>Falcon Building Products completes debt deal.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following two-part 144a private placement of high-yield debt from Falcon Building Products Inc was priced on Thursday via Smith Barney Inc (books) and BT Securities Corp, according to market sources.</p>
<p>Falcon Building Products makes items such as grills, diffusers and vent and chimney systems, for residential and commerical construction.</p>
